dct_title_s: Map showing the line of march from the coast to Adigerat
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Oriented with north to the left. Shows route of the British expedition in red. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 38, (1868), p. 12-49; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.38 1868
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1868.
